{"tid":2037464,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"張建宗：香港人有道義責任尊重國歌　不侮辱詆譭便不違法","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T04:48:58.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"8f5de83c3687b5efc3cab836f3fb4f320c98e2df","tid":2037464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:55:56.000Z","msg":"立法會今日（27日）恢復二讀辯論《國歌條例草案》（國歌法），政務司長張建宗在會議開始前見記者，表示希望今日會議取得進展可以落實，特區政府有憲制責任訂立國歌法，香港人有道義及責任尊重國歌，只要市民不公然侮辱及詆譭國歌便不會違法，市民不用擔心，亦不用上綱上線，與人權自由爭議無關，籲市民保持冷靜及理性討論。<br />\n<br />\n至於港區國安法，張建宗稱會努力向市民解釋有關立法目的及影響，只要依法行使權利，市民不用擔心人權受損，同時呼籲市民不要有負面想法，不要被誤導或被陰謀論影響，他強調立法是為了國家及香港的安全，同時為本港安居樂業。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又稱，維護國家安全是一國之責，沒有兩制之分，是國家和香港的共同責任。"},{"pid":"3ea0e74ddfd15ee367759ee178ff4198f466e22d","tid":2037464,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:56:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200527/s00001/1590549858257/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200527%2Fs00001%2F1590549858257%2F&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8UwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=bbdac739\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200527%2Fs00001%2F1590549858257%2F&h=ea07184f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200527/s00001/1590549858257/</a>"},{"pid":"967a82d0c80e384e22ef42dc4b37f6fe952383f0","tid":2037464,"uid":113187,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"香港政府<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有</span></strong></span>道義責任尊重香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daebc0630dc4e1f7f959876d5af679712de3c9bd","tid":2037464,"uid":206617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:57:42.000Z","msg":"上綱上線呢啲支那用語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\